256
00:18:04,676 --> 00:18:05,909
Cindy, I'm getting off work first.

257
00:18:05,909 --> 00:18:08,475
Okay, bye.

258
00:18:13,207 --> 00:18:14,842
I'm getting off work, too.

259
00:18:14,842 --> 00:18:17,242
You're leaving work without finishing your tasks?

260
00:18:17,242 --> 00:18:19,942
What can't be done today will be done tomorrow. Work won't run away.

261
00:18:19,974 --> 00:18:21,676
There are plans for tomorrow.

262
00:18:21,676 --> 00:18:24,875
And don't you want to learn how to schedule things from me?

263
00:18:24,875 --> 00:18:29,207
Yes, I do, but it's during working hours.

264
00:18:30,642 --> 00:18:34,108
Your efficiency isn't good when you work overtime. And it's also a violation of the labor law.

265
00:18:35,008 --> 00:18:37,408
Young people insist on not working overtime.

266
00:18:37,408 --> 00:18:39,208
Today, I've finally witnessed it.

267
00:18:39,208 --> 00:18:41,275
It's not like we insist on not working overtime.

268
00:18:41,275 --> 00:18:44,175
But rather... not to engage in meaningless time-wasting.

269
00:18:44,175 --> 00:18:47,241
Let's discuss what "meaningless" is, what is the definition of "meaningless"?

270
00:18:47,241 --> 00:18:50,142
- Off work! 
 - Meaningless is not having…

271
00:18:51,641 --> 00:18:53,875
Let's go, let's have dinner together.

272
00:18:53,875 --> 00:18:56,108
I can't, I have to work overtime today.

273
00:18:56,108 --> 00:18:58,175
How about another day?

274
00:18:58,175 --> 00:19:01,241
I thought you'd be less busy after becoming a secretary.

275
00:19:01,241 --> 00:19:02,875
I'm just getting the hang of the job.

276
00:19:02,875 --> 00:19:05,175
There're some things I want to handle first.

277
00:19:05,175 --> 00:19:09,442
But the restaurant I booked is the one you said you really wanted to try,

278
00:19:09,475 --> 00:19:11,908
but could never get a reservation for.

279
00:19:11,908 --> 00:19:13,207
Really?

280
00:19:13,207 --> 00:19:16,808
And have you bonded with the intern yet?

281
00:19:16,808 --> 00:19:17,941
She'll treat you to dinner.

282
00:19:17,941 --> 00:19:20,275
No. I still have to work overtime.

283
00:19:20,275 --> 00:19:23,608
I'll invite you to dinner another day then.

284
00:19:23,608 --> 00:19:26,108
Then I'll have to check out the place for you.

285
00:19:26,108 --> 00:19:30,107
I'll taste it for you, to see if it's good or not.

286
00:19:30,107 --> 00:19:33,208
Looking at the texture, and that flavor.

287
00:19:33,208 --> 00:19:36,708
Just go already, you're so annoying.

288
00:19:36,708 --> 00:19:38,141
- Okay, let it be. 
 - Sister Doula.

289
00:19:38,141 --> 00:19:40,908
- Do you want a lift? 
 - It's Sister Duomi.

290
00:19:40,908 --> 00:19:43,242
Sister Duomi, do you want a lift?

291
00:19:43,242 --> 00:19:44,909
How are you going to give me a lift? With what?

292
00:19:44,909 --> 00:19:48,075
I... I'll drive.

293
00:19:50,875 --> 00:19:52,474
I'm troubling you both.

294
00:19:52,474 --> 00:19:53,808
Please take good care of us.

295
00:19:53,808 --> 00:19:55,808
Dig in.

296
00:19:58,275 --> 00:20:00,741
- Mr. Xi, I'm late. 
 - Mr. Xi.

297
00:20:00,741 --> 00:20:02,575
Hello, I'm Guo.

298
00:20:02,575 --> 00:20:04,520
This is our Director Zheng and Director Li.

299
00:20:04,520 --> 00:20:05,509
- Director Zheng, Director Li, hello. 
 - Director Zheng, Director Li.

300
00:20:05,509 --> 00:20:09,076
This is Vice President Han and Manager Gao from Jingdu Construction.

301
00:20:11,308 --> 00:20:13,608
- A handsome guy and a beautiful lady. 
 - A person of good appearance, isn't it?

302
00:20:13,608 --> 00:20:16,142
Mr. Xi, I've specially brought a bottle of fine wine for you.

303
00:20:16,142 --> 00:20:19,375
And there's a gift too, very sincere, isn't it?

304
00:20:19,375 --> 00:20:21,208
However, this wine isn't suitable for drinking in large gulps.

305
00:20:21,208 --> 00:20:23,541
It's meant to be savored slowly.

306
00:20:23,541 --> 00:20:25,041
Are you looking down on us?

307
00:20:25,041 --> 00:20:27,508
Such a small bottle, it's hardly enough to drink, right?

308
00:20:27,508 --> 00:20:30,207
- Guo. 
 - Yes.

309
00:20:30,207 --> 00:20:32,741
Come, have a seat, don't be shy.

310
00:20:32,741 --> 00:20:33,942
Please sit.

311
00:20:33,942 --> 00:20:35,684
Sit down.

312
00:20:37,509 --> 00:20:41,408
Manager Gao. Please sit.

313
00:20:43,808 --> 00:20:45,875
Both of you, come here.

314
00:20:47,274 --> 00:20:48,742
Pour a glass then.

315
00:20:48,742 --> 00:20:50,008
Let me introduce this to you.

316
00:20:50,008 --> 00:20:52,576
What I have prepared here is 58 percent alcohol by volume.

317
00:20:52,576 --> 00:20:55,342
Just as passionate and fiery as I am.

318
00:20:55,342 --> 00:20:59,474
It's up to you whether to drink the whole bottle or go glass by glass. Either way is fine.

319
00:20:59,474 --> 00:21:02,575
You want to develop the new land my company has hunted down.

320
00:21:02,575 --> 00:21:04,676
It's very simple.

321
00:21:04,676 --> 00:21:06,841
As long as I feel good.

322
00:21:08,541 --> 00:21:10,974
I talk too crude, right?

323
00:21:10,974 --> 00:21:14,442
Not at all, Mr. Xi, I'll toast to you first.

324
00:21:14,442 --> 00:21:17,241
Here's to our successful cooperation.

325
00:21:17,241 --> 00:21:18,742
Sounds good.

326
00:21:18,742 --> 00:21:20,075
Mature and sensible.

327
00:21:20,075 --> 00:21:21,975
You get it, come on.

328
00:21:21,975 --> 00:21:25,541
Mr. Xi, I toast to you as well.

329
00:21:25,541 --> 00:21:27,775
No need, you have a special task today.

330
00:21:27,775 --> 00:21:30,242
You are responsible for taking care of these two elder brothers for me.

331
00:21:30,242 --> 00:21:33,175
Director Li. Director Zheng. I'll leave them to you.

332
00:21:33,175 --> 00:21:34,708
Director Li and Director Zheng.

333
00:21:34,708 --> 00:21:36,474
- Let me toast to you first. 
 - Mr. Xi, come on.

334
00:21:36,474 --> 00:21:41,308
Today, I just want to drink with girls who smell nice.

335
00:21:42,442 --> 00:21:45,007
Mr. Xi, you really have a sense of humor.

336
00:21:52,175 --> 00:21:53,909
- Come on, Director Li. 
 - Yes, here.

337
00:21:53,909 --> 00:21:55,609
- Another toast to you. 
 - Let's eat.

338
00:21:55,609 --> 00:21:56,808
Don't be polite.

339
00:21:56,808 --> 00:22:00,375
Try this meat, you're not afraid of getting fat, are you?

340
00:22:07,775 --> 00:22:11,007
I want to have a good drink with you.

341
00:22:11,708 --> 00:22:13,875
It's easier to pour this way.

342
00:22:28,041 --> 00:22:30,541
Are you okay? Have you been drinking too quickly?

343
00:22:30,541 --> 00:22:31,776
It's okay.

344
00:22:31,776 --> 00:22:32,942
Have some soup.

345
00:22:32,942 --> 00:22:34,442
Let me refill your drink.

346
00:22:34,442 --> 00:22:37,275
Take your time, drink slowly.

347
00:22:39,175 --> 00:22:41,009
Please excuse me for a moment.

348
00:22:41,941 --> 00:22:43,974
Had enough rest?

349
00:22:43,974 --> 00:22:45,409
Okay.

350
00:22:45,409 --> 00:22:50,109
Manager Gao, can I call you Xiaoyun?

351
00:22:50,709 --> 00:22:51,975
- Either is fine. 
 - Isn't it too intimate?

352
00:22:51,975 --> 00:22:53,509
Not at all.

353
00:23:00,808 --> 00:23:03,542
- I'm okay. 
 - No, you're too weak. Take good care of yourself.

354
00:23:03,542 --> 00:23:06,141
- Mr. Xi, I toast to you. 
 - Here.

355
00:23:06,909 --> 00:23:09,474
Hello, everyone.

356
00:23:14,509 --> 00:23:16,775
I'm Miss Gao's secretary.

357
00:23:16,775 --> 00:23:20,208
I'm Zhou, Vice President Han's secretary.

358
00:23:20,208 --> 00:23:22,142
You must be Mr. Xi.

359
00:23:24,875 --> 00:23:27,742
Manager Gao specifically instructed me

360
00:23:27,742 --> 00:23:30,141
that she's afraid that you'd drink too much and hurt your stomach.

361
00:23:30,141 --> 00:23:34,075
So, she told me to buy this to help you digest.

362
00:23:34,075 --> 00:23:36,141
Look how considerate Manager Gao is to you.

363
00:23:36,141 --> 00:23:38,141
Your colleague is so lively.

364
00:23:38,141 --> 00:23:41,541
It helps sobering up, so you can drink more.

365
00:23:41,541 --> 00:23:45,441
Okay, since Xiaoyun asked me to drink,

366
00:23:45,441 --> 00:23:47,474
then I'll drink it.

367
00:23:48,207 --> 00:23:50,609
You have to finish it.

368
00:23:50,609 --> 00:23:53,642
I'll drink the whole bottle.

369
00:24:08,442 --> 00:24:10,730
Done!

370
00:24:11,308 --> 00:24:13,108
Honestly, am I amazing or what?

371
00:24:13,108 --> 00:24:14,942
Then I shall be rewarded.

372
00:24:14,942 --> 00:24:16,775
I want a reward.

373
00:24:16,775 --> 00:24:18,442
- Mr. Xi, don't… 
 - I want the reward.

374
00:24:18,442 --> 00:24:20,475
I want a reward.

375
00:24:27,842 --> 00:24:29,409
Boss, are you okay?

376
00:24:29,409 --> 00:24:30,642
Guo.

377
00:24:30,642 --> 00:24:32,308
Hurry up.

378
00:24:34,942 --> 00:24:36,708
Boss, how are you?

379
00:24:36,708 --> 00:24:37,842
I'll take you to the restroom.

380
00:24:37,842 --> 00:24:39,708
- I'll take him to the restroom first. 
 - Come this way.

381
00:24:39,708 --> 00:24:41,474
Toilet is out the door, turn left.

382
00:24:41,474 --> 00:24:43,075
Be careful.

383
00:24:45,008 --> 00:24:47,342
Director Li. Director Zheng. Are you both okay?

384
00:24:47,342 --> 00:24:48,542
I think that's about it for today.

385
00:24:48,542 --> 00:24:50,942
- Zhou, let's send them back first. 
 - Okay.

386
00:24:50,942 --> 00:24:52,308
- Director Li, be careful. 
 - Come on.

387
00:24:52,308 --> 00:24:53,842
- Is it okay? 
 - Take it slow, right here.

388
00:24:53,842 --> 00:24:55,974
Cind, I'm leaving Manager Gao in your hands.

389
00:24:55,974 --> 00:24:59,041
- Be careful, this way. 
 - Come. 
 - Careful, slowly.

390
00:24:59,041 --> 00:25:00,742
Watch for safety, walk carefully.

391
00:25:00,742 --> 00:25:02,209
- This way. 
 - This way, please.

392
00:25:02,209 --> 00:25:04,000
Be careful.

393
00:25:04,742 --> 00:25:07,676
You've also had too much to drink, haven't you?

394
00:25:12,942 --> 00:25:15,308
- Be careful. 
 - Thank you.

395
00:25:19,942 --> 00:25:21,509
The car is here.

396
00:25:21,509 --> 00:25:25,274
Sorry, driver, could you please open the door?

397
00:25:26,242 --> 00:25:28,242
Meng Heng.

398
00:25:28,242 --> 00:25:30,742
You're actually driving an uber?

399
00:25:30,742 --> 00:25:32,207
Yeah, it's a part-time job.

400
00:25:32,207 --> 00:25:34,008
This car isn't cheap.

401
00:25:34,008 --> 00:25:35,942
You couldn't be a second-generation rich kid, could you?

402
00:25:35,942 --> 00:25:39,208
It's debt. I bought this car with a loan.

403
00:25:40,148 --> 00:25:43,174
- Come on, get in the car first. 
 - Come on, be careful.

404
00:25:44,009 --> 00:25:45,009
Okay, come.

405
00:25:45,009 --> 00:25:47,230
Be careful.

406
00:25:47,875 --> 00:25:49,909
Here, your bag.

407
00:25:49,909 --> 00:25:51,474
Thank you.

408
00:25:52,775 --> 00:25:54,974
Why did you come here?

409
00:25:54,974 --> 00:25:57,641
The Vice President called me for a rescue.

410
00:26:03,909 --> 00:26:05,275
- What should we do? 
 - Zhou.

411
00:26:05,275 --> 00:26:08,075
- Cindy, over here. 
 - What did the Vice President call us here for?

412
00:26:08,075 --> 00:26:09,342
It's not to fend off drinks, is it?

413
00:26:09,342 --> 00:26:12,009
No, he called us here to help.

414
00:26:12,009 --> 00:26:13,275
- Help? 
 - Yes.

415
00:26:13,275 --> 00:26:15,008
Who? Gao Shuangyun?

416
00:26:15,008 --> 00:26:16,842
Manager Gao, right.

417
00:26:16,842 --> 00:26:18,342
No, then why don't you just go in and take the person away?

418
00:26:18,342 --> 00:26:20,208
What did you call me here for?

419
00:26:20,208 --> 00:26:22,409
If it were that simple, I wouldn't have had to look for you.

420
00:26:22,409 --> 00:26:23,909
The Vice President just gave special instructions, saying

421
00:26:23,909 --> 00:26:28,474
we have to take Manager Gao away without offending Mr. Xi.

422
00:26:31,009 --> 00:26:33,108
And do you know what was even more outrageous just now?

423
00:26:33,108 --> 00:26:37,542
I just heard that Mr. Guo next to Mr. Xi just snuck out,

424
00:26:37,542 --> 00:26:39,542
and made a call to book a room.

425
00:26:39,542 --> 00:26:41,574
What?!

426
00:26:42,641 --> 00:26:44,208
I know Mr. Xi is a lecher.

427
00:26:44,208 --> 00:26:47,074
He even has the audacity to this extent.

428
00:26:47,074 --> 00:26:48,307
This is criminal, you know.

429
00:26:48,307 --> 00:26:51,942
Manager Gao has sacrificed so much for the company. I really can't bear it.

430
00:26:53,008 --> 00:26:55,575
It's not worth it. I mean it's not worth it.

431
00:26:55,575 --> 00:26:57,641
Anyway, I just can't think of any solution.

432
00:26:57,641 --> 00:26:59,708
Do you have any ideas? Please help.

433
00:26:59,708 --> 00:27:01,742
Did they drink a lot?

434
00:27:01,742 --> 00:27:03,942
Seems like they drank quite a bit.

435
00:27:03,942 --> 00:27:06,342
I think I have a way. That, help me take it for a moment.

436
00:27:06,342 --> 00:27:10,408
- Wait for me, I'll be right back. 
 - What?

437
00:27:10,408 --> 00:27:13,141
What method? Tell me first.

438
00:27:13,141 --> 00:27:15,470
I have to say,

439
00:27:15,470 --> 00:27:18,190
you really know how to adapt to the situation.

440
00:27:18,742 --> 00:27:20,108
And luckily you vomited last time.

441
00:27:20,108 --> 00:27:22,074
Otherwise, I wouldn't know the little trick.

442
00:27:22,074 --> 00:27:24,908
- I didn't vomit. 
 - Yes, you did.

443
00:27:25,676 --> 00:27:29,742
Anyway, I still want to thank you.

444
00:27:33,142 --> 00:27:36,108
Right, remember to buy me a gift tomorrow.

445
00:27:36,108 --> 00:27:38,309
I also want to thank Zhou.

446
00:27:38,309 --> 00:27:39,374
Okay.

447
00:27:39,374 --> 00:27:42,708
Also, next time, no matter the occasion,

448
00:27:42,708 --> 00:27:44,108
even if you don't need my company,

449
00:27:44,108 --> 00:27:46,808
you must tell me who will be attending and where the location is.

450
00:27:46,842 --> 00:27:49,074
You have to let me know, okay?

451
00:27:50,542 --> 00:27:52,109
I'm leaving.

452
00:28:04,974 --> 00:28:06,541
Finally, I know why you have to leave work on the dot.

453
00:28:06,541 --> 00:28:08,641
So, you have a side job.

454
00:28:08,641 --> 00:28:10,641
The culture of overtime is wrong to begin with.

455
00:28:10,641 --> 00:28:14,142
As for the side job, it's because I like to explore different professions,

456
00:28:14,142 --> 00:28:17,376
and various ways to earn money.

457
00:28:18,608 --> 00:28:21,275
But your car seems to be expensive.

458
00:28:21,275 --> 00:28:23,408
If it was bought with a loan,

459
00:28:23,408 --> 00:28:25,474
then can you actually make money like this?

460
00:28:25,474 --> 00:28:27,409
The money hasn't disappeared.

461
00:28:27,409 --> 00:28:30,374
It's just becoming the way I like.

462
00:28:30,374 --> 00:28:33,509
I really don't understand what you young people think.

463
00:28:34,442 --> 00:28:36,041
I'll take you home.

464
00:28:36,041 --> 00:28:37,775
I'll give you a 20 percent discount.

465
00:28:37,775 --> 00:28:39,042
20 percent off?

466
00:28:39,042 --> 00:28:41,842
Thank you for your kindness today.

467
00:28:41,842 --> 00:28:43,509
Can't do anything about it, after all.

468
00:28:43,509 --> 00:28:45,675
Handsome and kind-hearted, you know.

469
00:28:47,708 --> 00:28:49,807
What's so funny?

470
00:28:52,509 --> 00:28:54,309
I'm not giving you a discount anymore.

471
00:28:54,309 --> 00:28:57,676
All right, I'm just kidding. I want the discount.

472
00:28:57,676 --> 00:29:01,942
- Get off the car. 
 - No, I'll fasten my seatbelt

473
00:29:01,942 --> 00:29:04,620
Go home by yourself.

474
00:29:48,905 --> 00:29:50,950
[Uncle]

475
00:29:59,308 --> 00:30:03,742
Thank our most handsome Vice President Han for rescuing me.

476
00:30:03,742 --> 00:30:05,774
It's so good to have you.

477
00:30:07,275 --> 00:30:08,574
You're my woman.

478
00:30:08,574 --> 00:30:11,574
It's only right for me to protect you.

479
00:30:11,574 --> 00:30:15,141
I just love hearing you say that all the time.

480
00:30:16,775 --> 00:30:19,874
"My woman."

481
00:30:21,041 --> 00:30:24,174
After hearing that, there's a feeling of being owned,

482
00:30:24,174 --> 00:30:28,142
being protected, being admired,

483
00:30:28,142 --> 00:30:30,708
being exclusively cherished and loved by a man.

484
00:30:30,708 --> 00:30:32,942
The feeling of being cared for.

485
00:30:32,942 --> 00:30:36,708
Because you truly are the woman I cherish, love

486
00:30:36,708 --> 00:30:39,274
and protect, the only woman.

487
00:30:43,842 --> 00:30:47,807
So, are you coming over?

488
00:30:47,808 --> 00:30:50,941
I'll wait for you. My man.

489
00:30:53,908 --> 00:30:56,041
I really want to come over.

490
00:30:56,041 --> 00:30:58,909
But I drank too much just now, feeling a bit dazed.

491
00:30:58,909 --> 00:31:04,008
Moreover, I accidentally broke our house's code lock.

492
00:31:04,008 --> 00:31:06,441
I'm waiting for rescue now.

493
00:31:07,342 --> 00:31:10,750
Then just stand at the door as punishment.

494
00:31:11,308 --> 00:31:13,480
I'm going to take a nice bath.

495
00:31:14,574 --> 00:31:17,875
You saying that is tempting fate, you know. Be careful.

496
00:31:19,541 --> 00:31:22,408
All right. You also drank quite a bit today.

497
00:31:22,442 --> 00:31:24,241
Rest early.

498
00:31:25,809 --> 00:31:27,542
Bye.

499
00:31:27,542 --> 00:31:29,042
Good night.

500
00:31:55,974 --> 00:31:57,742
You don't need to keep hurrying me.

501
00:31:57,742 --> 00:32:01,674
I'll give you what I owe you.

502
00:32:04,308 --> 00:32:05,842
Got it.

503
00:32:18,908 --> 00:32:20,509
Thank you for giving me a lift back.

504
00:32:20,509 --> 00:32:24,141
You can just pull up to the side by that door entrance later,

505
00:32:24,141 --> 00:32:26,042
and I'll give you a five-star rating and a tip.

506
00:32:26,042 --> 00:32:28,008
- I'll give them to you, rest assured. 
 - Okay.

507
00:32:28,008 --> 00:32:31,608
You can come into the office later tomorrow. I will inform the manager.

508
00:32:31,608 --> 00:32:33,075
You can stop right here at the entrance.

509
00:32:33,075 --> 00:32:35,509
- Yes, where? 
 - Here, right here.

510
00:32:35,509 --> 00:32:36,641
- You've passed it. 
 - I've passed it?

511
