606
00:39:22,408 --> 00:39:24,308
Five hundred?

607
00:39:26,174 --> 00:39:27,374
Right.

608
00:39:27,374 --> 00:39:29,541
Didn't the manager say that you could come into the office later yesterday?

609
00:39:29,541 --> 00:39:31,341
