614
00:39:42,474 --> 00:39:44,675
I have so much work. Of course, I need to come early.

615
00:39:44,675 --> 00:39:45,974
You've got a lot of work?

616
00:39:45,974 --> 00:39:47,575
Where?

617
00:39:47,575 --> 00:39:49,008
- I… 
 - Did the manager come yet?

618
00:39:49,008 --> 00:39:51,442
I have a document for her to sign.

619
00:39:52,508 --> 00:39:55,309
She drank too much yesterday, she'll come in later. You can give it to me.

620
00:39:55,309 --> 00:39:57,876
No need, I'll wait for the manager and deliver it myself.

621
00:39:57,876 --> 00:39:59,407
Thank you.

